{"tid":1717531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[建築撚] 所有set rb同前線手足入","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T11:25:13.000Z","uid":63912,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a255dc36f87479890ae24ad957722c0f49e246e3","tid":1717531,"uid":63912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"啱先有個工程fd話冇ac想我幫手post<br />\n佢話作為建築撚見到冇用盡每一舊磚同英泥 好浪費<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我剛剛諗到用磚堆成一個呎半高嘅金字塔<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以擋到車</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">popo用腳無辦法一腳踢得散</span></strong><br />\n二戰用嚟擋坦克，名為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Dragons Teeth</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j880Kkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj880Kkn.jpg&h=116c8569&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n搭住簡化版<br />\n但點黐實啲磚？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FCT4kn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FCT4kn.jpg&h=92769463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依種paving block 其實好實正<br />\n排兩層 磚與磚中間落小小泥<br />\n4個鐘後基本人推都唔冧<br />\n捱到聽朝就要用鎚扑先拆到<br />\n依家咁樣係浪費英泥<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2497937b50fc52e110c2efcc435da17bcec8d956","tid":1717531,"uid":63912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"Dragons Teeth<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\